<s> [INST] You are an expert in Natural Language Inference (NLI). Please list all possible explanations why the the following statement is true (entailment) given the context below without introductory phrases. 
Context: Their supplies scarce, their harvest meager, and their spirit broken, they abandoned the fort in 1858. 
Statement: Their supplies remained very low and hard to maintain. 
Answer: [/INST] 1. The supplies were already scarce when they abandoned the fort.
2. The situation of having low and hard to maintain supplies contributed to their decision to abandon the fort.
3. There was no improvement in their supply situation between 1858 and when the statement was made, thus the supplies remained scarce.
4. The meager harvest would have further reduced their supplies, making them even harder to maintain.
5. The language used in the statement implies a continuation of the scarcity and difficulty in maintaining supplies, aligning with the context.</s>